<title>Edit contact details</title>

  <p>Editing contact details helps you keep the information in your address
  book up to date and complete.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Select the contact from your contact list.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">Edit</gui> in the top-rigth corner of
      <app>Contacts</app>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Edit the contact details.</p>
      <p>To add a <gui>detail</gui> such as a new phone number or email
      address, press <gui style="button">Add Detail</gui> and select the field
      that you want to add.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Press <gui style="button">Done</gui> to finish editing the
      contact.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

<note>
  <p>In the case of linked contacts, you can edit a profile by clicking on the
   profile's avatar.</p>
</note>

